docs.text: Welcome to the Encyclopedia of P@tnicRoom! This site is for Players if you are a Developer and looking for the Docs click here Introduction You can find here all kinds of Information to Game elements. We encourage to use this collection while playing as a handy to get needed information. This content can also be found in the game via the Rest-mode, its no cheating tto make your experience more comfortable :) Getting started If you want to dive deep into the Concepts and Systems of P@nicRoom, we recommend to start at the different types of Game elements . Something that can expand your understanding is the meaning of parts in a Kitset . Overviews Are you looking for something? Here are some suggestions to start searching: Tiles are the more simple stuff on a Map Interactables are like Tiles on a map but have a rather more complex usage Actors are like players capable of doing things, often humanlike but not neccesarrily Kitsets are integral for survival and progression, they are puzzled together by 3 parts Quickreferences Tiles by Group Base Kitparts Mod Kitparts Appendix Kitparts Race of Actors Role of Actors Specialty of Actors
